ano, @Malevolent Voidheart, @INVADA, @Armok, @Kazoo kid, @Agent Kirin, @MWH, @BigIronJuliette, @dr.nightmares2.0, @SpeedyDragon9k and Kumochan for the amazing hats! (If your hat needs to be adjusted or nudged, let me know as well)\n\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/xmQOfth.png[/img]\n\n- Added the [b]Factory Handbook[/b], a basic tutorial interface for the factory progression.\n- Added the Liquid Pump, an automatic pump that extracts liquid from below.\n- Added the Factory Locker, a smaller storage container for automation.\n\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯\n\n- Added Animus themed weapons.\n- Added Geoelectra themed building blocks.\n- Added the Arioforged Dagger, a tier 5 throwing weapon. (Credits to @shawnty5227)\n- Added new dialog for Exousian police npcs, as well as reworked several codex entries. (Credits to @INVADA)\n- Added more colored variants for Aurea, Exousia, Orion, Titancorp, Bleuark and Luye tiles. (Credits to @dr.nightmares2.0)\n- Added the Sloped Rusty Panel block and Neo Synthite Flooring. (Credits to @dr.nightmares2.0)\n- Added colored variants for several Exousia tiles. (Credits to @Luyia)\n- Added a beam up option for the Galactic Map, credits to @MWH.\n- Added shield generators to Voltaic Forts and Exousian cities.\n- Added new codex books for bosses.\n\n Lastly, please give us feedbacks & suggestions in our Discord Server! Thanks for your support as always :D\n\n\n\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n[h1]Arcana, a Mystical Universe[/h1]\n\nArcana is a growing techno-magic themed Starbound mod that features a vast amount of added content, including:\n\n[list]\n[*]28+ new planets\n\n[*]80+ custom weapons\n\n[*]80+ armor pieces and cosmetics\n\n[*]600+ new tiles and objects\n[/list]\n\nArcana is also constantly updating with new contents, aiming to always provide new magical elements for the star explorers to find.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]New Bosses & Monsters[/h1]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/QuJiMjr